4. Substituir el valor de `TOUCH_CAL_DATA` a `config.h`:
   ```cpp
   #define TOUCH_CAL_DATA  { 281, 3535, 347, 3583, 7 }
   ```
5. Re-compilar i flashejar el firmware complet.

